# Icon PNGs (16/32/48/128) are generated by scripts/gen-icons.mjs, not committed
# by hand. See IMPLEMENTATION.md → "Icons": gen-icons.mjs must be extended with a
# `devdata` entry before the first build, or `action.default_icon` in
# wxt.config.ts (and the auto-discovered top-level icons map) will 404.
